                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Lower half of broken tall rectangular column, leaving a jagged, slightly diagonal top edge. Entabulature on bottom third of altar, which is wider than the main body. Other than its broken top, the rest of the altar is in relatively good condition, although worn on various edges.</p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.marble" ref="https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html">Marble</material>
